<item>
            <title>[SOLR-3933] Distributed commits are not guaranteed to be ordered within a request.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3933</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Update requests that also include a commit may do adds or deletes after the commit - it&apos;s a race.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This would most likely affect concurrent update server or bulk add methods - but it&apos;s still a race for a single doc update or delete that includes a commit as well.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
